April 22, 2014Pattern Health’s vision is to make healthcare more efficient and effective through connected care and research products. Naturally, this involves working with information that is important to you, and we appreciate the trust you have placed in us to protect your privacy.
This Privacy Policy applies to information collected or processed by Pattern Health Technologies, Inc (“Pattern Health”, “our”, “we” or “us”) via our devices, applications, software, websites, APIs, and our general dealings with customers through email and other forms of communication regarding our products and services (the “Services”). This policy explains what data we collect, how we use it, your individual rights, and the measures we take to keep your information safe.
Information we collect, why we collect it, and how the information is used
Information provided by you
