Job Application
If you apply for a job you provide us with your resume and other personal information which are necessary to be able to process your application and contact you about an employment opportunity.
Through normal use of our Services
Through normal use of our Services, you may enter information such as your personal health information, photos, notes, your health goals, your name, email address, birth date, gender and other sensitive information. The Services use this information to allow you to track and share your health data. You may also authorize certain third party health applications and services to sync your data from those services with your Pattern Health account. You may encrypt information on your mobile device by setting a passcode on iOS or enabling device encryption on Android.
